text: Madushika Methtananda (born 24 July 1994) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. In March 2019, she was named in Sri Lanka's squad for their series against England. She made her Women's Twenty20 International cricket (WT20I) debut for Sri Lanka against England Women on 28 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan women cricketers Category:Sri Lanka women Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
